incredible news.

14:54.995 --> 14:58.563
Cookie has agreed to manage you

14:58.565 --> 15:00.098
and take over the production

15:00.100 --> 15:01.332
of your next album.

15:01.334 --> 15:02.867
Uh-uh, Lucious.
Forget it.

15:02.869 --> 15:04.936
