work with top people.

15:04.938 --> 15:07.572
That's how I sold over
100 million records.

15:07.574 --> 15:09.841
But in the last five years,
it's been none.

15:09.843 --> 15:13.011
That's, like, maybe the
audience has forgotten you.

15:14.546 --> 15:17.882
Okay, here's what you will
get with me:

15:17.884 --> 15:20.952
someone who
appreciates your gift

15:20.954 --> 15:22.854
and who knows
what to do with it.

15:22.856 --> 15:24.956
I won't sleep until
you're back on the charts.

15:24.958 --> 15:27.358
I tell you,
Cookie is your best bet.

15:27.360 --> 15:29.861
I mean, she's been
begging to manage you,

15:29.863 --> 15:33.131
she's your biggest fan
and she's hungry.

15:33.133 --> 15:35.066
I need a real producer.

15:35.068 --> 15:36.534
Hip boy-- Timbaland.

15:36.536 --> 15:38.269
No, no, no.
They're afraid of you.

15:38.271 --> 15:40.772
I mean, I think it's time
we start building new bridges.

15:40.774 --> 15:43.074
You listen to me, darling.

15:43.076 --> 15:46.711
When Empire started out,
it was my record sales

15:46.713 --> 15:48.780
that kept the lights on
in that black shack.

15:48.782 --> 15:51.716
My back catalog alone
floated you.

15:51.718 --> 15:53.952
I opened your company up
into a world you never knew.

15:53.954 --> 15:56.721
And now... oh, you've
got this nightclub,

15:56.723 --> 15:58.256
fashion lines,

15:58.258 --> 16:00.058
Empire champagne?

16:00.060 --> 16:01.592
And what do I get?

16:01.594 --> 16:04.762
My career handed over
to an ex-con.

16:04.764 --> 16:06.998
Elle...
No, Lucious, no.

16:07.000 --> 16:09.801
