17:41.261 --> 17:43.594
I know. Mm-hmm.

17:43.596 --> 17:45.563
The first thing
you think about every morning

17:45.565 --> 17:47.231
is where you're getting
your first hit from.

17:47.233 --> 17:49.033
And if your dealer
ain't holding,

17:49.035 --> 17:50.868
