18:00.346 --> 18:02.880
I had to block out everything
so that I could survive.

18:02.882 --> 18:04.515
You got me through.

18:04.517 --> 18:06.451
I got to the top by myself.

18:06.453 --> 18:08.286
No one helped me,

18:08.288 --> 18:10.955
