Shut up.

22:23.609 --> 22:24.842
(chuckles)

22:25.977 --> 22:28.112
That girl is...
This song is going to be

22:28.114 --> 22:29.447
a monster hit.

22:29.449 --> 22:30.648
Why don't you be the first one

22:30.650 --> 22:32.116
to introduce it to the world?

22:33.518 --> 22:37.388
I'm only doing this
because you two are hilarious.

22:39.057 --> 22:41.292
What's the name of the song?

22:41.294 --> 22:44.028
It says you were awarded
the Silver Star of Excellence

22:44.030 --> 22:48.065
for courage while under fire
stationed in Iraq?

22:48.067 --> 22:50.534
Yes, sir. I was there
for four years

22:50.536 --> 22:53.537
as team leader
of a tactical recovery platoon.

22:53.539 --> 22:55.673
What did you recover?

22:55.675 --> 22:58.075
That's classified, sir.

22:58.077 --> 22:59.677
(chuckles)

22:59.679 --> 23:02.079
I have 12 years' experience
as a Navy Seal

23:02.081 --> 23:04.248
specializing
in close quarter combat,

23:04.250 --> 23:07.551
hostage rescue/recovery,
and antiterrorism.

23:07.553 --> 23:09.153
I've overseen
personal security

23:09.155 --> 23:10.821
for figures such as yourself,

23:10.823 --> 23:12.390
executives, religious leaders,

23:12.392 --> 23:15.760
and others who face
high-stakes security challenges.

23:17.229 --> 23:20.731
You know, my company's
in the middle of an IPO launch.

23:20.733 --> 23:23.367
Yes, sir. It's a great time
to beef up your security.

23:23.369 --> 23:25.870
A lot of friends,
but I got a whole lot of enemies

23:25.872 --> 23:28.105
that would love
to see this IPO not happen.

23:28.107 --> 23:30.541
Well, I've done
a thorough review

23:30.543 --> 23:33.110
of both your home
and your corporate headquarters.

23:33.112 --> 23:35.446
Really?
Yes, sir.

23:35.448 --> 23:36.714
What'd you find?

23:36.716 --> 23:38.682
That this entire
building and your home

23:38.684 --> 23:40.785
are one giant breach.

23:40.787 --> 23:44.054
