23:45.391 --> 23:47.625
with black holes
about a mile wide,

23:47.627 --> 23:49.226
the northwest gate
sensor can be tripped

23:49.228 --> 23:50.694
by anybody with a cell phone,

23:50.696 --> 23:53.130
Hell, no. and the
night security detail

23:53.132 --> 23:54.899
looks more
like a donut commercial

23:54.901 --> 23:58.602
than a threat deterrent.
I would start from scratch, sir.

23:58.604 --> 24:00.604
I like how you do your recon.

24:00.606 --> 24:02.106
Let's get you to work, sir.

24:02.108 --> 24:03.407
Mm.

24:03.409 --> 24:05.609
Thank you, Mr. Lyon.

24:05.611 --> 24:06.610
