24:48.855 --> 24:50.287
Shh.
Come on, Jamal.

24:50.289 --> 24:52.756
Please. I need your help.

24:52.758 --> 24:55.426
I can't get the hook right.
Hakeem, I don't care.

24:55.428 --> 24:57.595
You should have thought about all
that before. Thought of what?

24:57.597 --> 24:59.363
How long did you think
that I would just sit around

24:59.365 --> 25:01.632
and let you disrespect our mother,
when all she's trying to do

25:01.634 --> 25:03.200
is help you grow up?

25:03.202 --> 25:05.436
How long did you think that
I would just let you use me?

25:05.438 --> 25:07.271
I don't care.

25:07.273 --> 25:10.608
Ma, I'm gonna leave.

25:10.610 --> 25:11.876
Thank you, baby.
I love you.

25:11.878 --> 25:13.777
Call you tomorrow.
Okay.

25:17.816 --> 25:20.684
VERNON: All right, let's
go over this one more time.

25:20.686 --> 25:23.120
I was over by the river.
Which river?

25:23.122 --> 25:24.989
The Hudson. Uptown.

25:24.991 --> 25:27.057
Near West Harlem Piers.

25:27.059 --> 25:28.993
And?
