at a time,

25:42.475 --> 25:44.208
so nobody notices.

25:44.210 --> 25:45.543
And who am I

25:45.545 --> 25:47.044
taking the fall for?

25:47.046 --> 25:48.812
Don't you worry about that.
Just make sure

25:48.814 --> 25:51.282
you don't ever deviate
from the story.

25:53.084 --> 25:54.285
Easy.

26:08.033 --> 26:09.433
Babe?
Yeah, baby?

26:09.435 --> 26:11.068
"Keep Your Money"
is still trending.

26:11.070 --> 26:14.238
