(chuckles)

26:14.240 --> 26:17.041
Man, Cookie
really hooked that up.

26:17.043 --> 26:20.611
I swear, that woman is the
ultimate hustler. Yep.

26:22.581 --> 26:25.616
Hey. Why are people tweeting
about some...

26:25.618 --> 26:28.552
satellite radio interview you're
supposed to have this weekend?

26:28.554 --> 26:31.388
